==1928 Transactions==
*[[December 12]]: Sold [[Johnny Butler]] to the [[Chicago Cubs]]
*[[June 8]]: Traded [[Charlie Hargreaves]] to the [[Pittsburgh Pirates]] for [[Joe Harris (baseball)|Joe Harris]] and [[Johnny Gooch]]
*[[June 23]]: Sold [[Howard Freigau]] to the [[Atlanta Braves|Boston Braves]]

